[{"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/0deb/1c54/413_large.png?m=1610122546", "name": "programming", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/0deb/1c54/413_normal.png?m=1610122546", "title": "编程", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programming", "topics": 1420, "footer": "", "header": "Have fun and make money and art.", "title_alternative": "Programming", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/0deb/1c54/413_mini.png?m=1610122546", "stars": 2296, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 413, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 75489, "username": "stevenrao", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/stevenrao", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/50a3/beeb/75489_mini.png?m=1414069147", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/50a3/beeb/75489_normal.png?m=1414069147", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/50a3/beeb/75489_large.png?m=1414069147", "created": 1411967901, "last_modified": 1414069147, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "tairan2006", "last_touched": 1775380386, "title": "AI 写代码真香喷；以后只要产品经理就可以了", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1203613", "created": 1775356210, "deleted": 0, "content": "## 🚀 只用了 2 天，一行代码没写\r\n\r\n说出来你可能不信，这个项目我一行代码都没写。\r\n\r\n我的工作流程是这样的：\r\n1. 📝 和 AI 聊需求，确定要做什么功能\r\n2. 📄 写成详细的 PRD 文档\r\n3. 🤖 交给编程 AI Agent 去实现\r\n4. 🔍 我来测试，提 Bug ，提需求\r\n5. � 循环往复，直到满意\r\n\r\n**就这样，2 天时间，口袋 BBS 诞生了！**\r\n\r\n### 总共代码行 \r\n| Language           | files | blank | comment | code  |\r\n|--------------------|-------|-------|---------|-------|\r\n| Go                 | 84    | 1944  | 1491    | 10494 |\r\n| Vuejs Component    | 39    | 1131  | 2137    | 8594  |\r\n| JavaScript         | 23    | 138   | 248     | 3347  |\r\n| CSS                | 2     | 25    | 19      | 123   |\r\n| SUM:               | 148   | 3238  | 3895    | 22558 |\r\n\r\n## *它只有一个独立的二进制程序，linux 叫 bbsgo ，window 叫 bbsgo.exe ;集成管理后台，主站，本地数据库于一体； 可以放在 U 盘，随时运行；\r\n不得不感叹 AI 的遍历，AI 为了避免初次打开网页光秃秃的没有内容，还贴心的帮我初始化一批图文并茂的数据，太贴心。*\r\n\r\n*代码开源： https://github.com/mageg-x/bbsgo*\r\n\r\n*在线演示： https://bbs.mageg.cn/*", "content_rendered": "<h2>🚀 只用了 2 天，一行代码没写</h2>\n<p>说出来你可能不信，这个项目我一行代码都没写。</p>\n<p>我的工作流程是这样的：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>📝 和 AI 聊需求，确定要做什么功能</li>\n<li>📄 写成详细的 PRD 文档</li>\n<li>🤖 交给编程 AI Agent 去实现</li>\n<li>🔍 我来测试，提 Bug ，提需求</li>\n<li>� 循环往复，直到满意</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>就这样，2 天时间，口袋 BBS 诞生了！</strong></p>\n<h3>总共代码行</h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Language</th>\n<th>files</th>\n<th>blank</th>\n<th>comment</th>\n<th>code</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Go</td>\n<td>84</td>\n<td>1944</td>\n<td>1491</td>\n<td>10494</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Vuejs Component</td>\n<td>39</td>\n<td>1131</td>\n<td>2137</td>\n<td>8594</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>JavaScript</td>\n<td>23</td>\n<td>138</td>\n<td>248</td>\n<td>3347</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>CSS</td>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>25</td>\n<td>19</td>\n<td>123</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>SUM:</td>\n<td>148</td>\n<td>3238</td>\n<td>3895</td>\n<td>22558</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table><h2>*它只有一个独立的二进制程序，linux 叫 bbsgo ，window 叫 bbsgo.exe ;集成管理后台，主站，本地数据库于一体； 可以放在 U 盘，随时运行；</h2>\n<p>不得不感叹 AI 的遍历，AI 为了避免初次打开网页光秃秃的没有内容，还贴心的帮我初始化一批图文并茂的数据，太贴心。*</p>\n<p><em>代码开源： <a href=\"https://github.com/mageg-x/bbsgo\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://github.com/mageg-x/bbsgo</a></em></p>\n<p><em>在线演示： <a href=\"https://bbs.mageg.cn/\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://bbs.mageg.cn/</a></em></p>\n", "last_modified": 1775356644, "replies": 37, "id": 1203613}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/9226/2bf9/941_large.png?m=1475387237", "name": "rime", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/9226/2bf9/941_normal.png?m=1475387237", "title": "中州韻", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/rime", "topics": 147, "footer": "", "header": "聪明的输入法懂我心意", "title_alternative": "RIME", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/9226/2bf9/941_mini.png?m=1475387237", "stars": 145, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 941, "parent_node_name": "ime"}, "member": {"id": 717268, "username": "DearFox", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/DearFox", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/f8df6c11f09cfe84cba114f98f24da53?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/f8df6c11f09cfe84cba114f98f24da53?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/f8df6c11f09cfe84cba114f98f24da53?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1730037069, "last_modified": 1774343424, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "xiangyuecn", "last_touched": 1775378271, "title": "是不是折腾输入法的尽头都是回归原生输入法?", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1203545", "created": 1775299058, "deleted": 0, "content": "去年折腾 rime 输入法,给电脑,手机,家人的,都弄 rime,刚开始还兴致勃勃,有时间就同步一下词库啥的,现在半年没动过,看见用的输入法方案更新,都懒的下载,总是感觉麻烦.还不如用自带的啥都不管", "content_rendered": "<p>去年折腾 rime 输入法,给电脑,手机,家人的,都弄 rime,刚开始还兴致勃勃,有时间就同步一下词库啥的,现在半年没动过,看见用的输入法方案更新,都懒的下载,总是感觉麻烦.还不如用自带的啥都不管</p>\n", "last_modified": 1775299058, "replies": 32, "id": 1203545}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/1fc2/1400/864_large.png?m=1775086598", "name": "promotions", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/1fc2/1400/864_normal.png?m=1775086598", "title": "推广", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/promotions", "topics": 10950, "footer": "", "header": "来自厂商的推广活动类主题，会被归类到这个节点。希望有情怀的产商们在发布推广内容时，主动选择发布到本节点下。点击 <a href=\"/help/node\">这里</a> 阅读 V2EX 的节点使用指南。", "title_alternative": "Promotions", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/1fc2/1400/864_mini.png?m=1775086598", "stars": 1161, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 864, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 51, "username": "daqing", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/daqing", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "daqing", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "关注我，一起在编程技术领域里开荒。", "bio": "程序员，交易员，独立开发者，软件生意人。\r\n\r\nvx: 420771712", "avatar_mini": "https://cd